s=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3615293\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104puj1665702639291.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/puj1665702639291.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/puj1665702639291.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"puj1665702639291\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Extended Auto Select (\n                              XAutoSelect)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether all the text in the current field is selected if it gets focus using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$prompt</span> ProcScript function. <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default)\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"puj1665702639291__p_d103412e1_d103413e1_d103414e1\">XAutoSelect<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"puj1665702639291__section_l44_k43_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549283e77\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"puj1665702639291__table_d12197e1_d12198e1_d12199e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported in Grid?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes for Edit Box</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"puj1665702639291__section_udw_l43_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549283e141\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"puj1665702639291__p_d103421e1_d103422e1_d103423e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Extended Auto Select</span>\n        property has effect only if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Auto Select</span> is on. By default, it is\n        cleared.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"puj1665702639291__p_d103424e1_d103425e1_d103426e1\">If <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>, all the text in the widget\n        is selected when the field gets focus as a result of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$prompt</span> to the\n        current field.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"puj1665702639291__section_xnm_443_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549283e165\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"puj1665702639291__pre_a4l_q43_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"xautoselect=true\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"puj1665702639291__section_bfq_q43_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d549283e174\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"puj1665702639291__ul_nfz_r43_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"puj1665702639291__li_d42032e1_d42033e1_d42034e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"klb1688454363706.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/klb1688454363706.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a Form or Report.\">EditBox</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"puj1665702639291__li_d42035e1_d42036e1_d42037e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qwk1688451210612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qwk1688451210612.html\" title=\"The urtfeditbox widget is used to display and edit text as Rich Text Format (RTF), which supports formatting such as font and color attributes, text alignment, indentation, and lists. Uniface provides a logical widget called RichEditBox, which is mapped to urtfeditbox.\">urtfeditbox (RichEditBox)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/plb1718886888754.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$prompt</a><p>Return or set the position for the cursor in the Form when the current ProcScript module ends.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/glz1665702631024.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Auto Select (autoselect)</a><p>Determines whether the text in the widget is selected when the field gets focus.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615293\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615293\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Extended Auto Select ( XAutoSelect) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Extended Auto Select ( XAutoSelect) This property determines whether all the text in the current field is selected if it gets focus using the $prompt ProcScript function. True or False (default) XAutoSelect = \" True | False \" Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? Yes for Edit Box Dependencies: None Description The Extended Auto Select property has effect only if Auto Select is on. By default, it is cleared. If True , all the text in the widget is selected when the field gets focus as a result of $prompt to the current field. Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"xautoselect=true\" Copy Applies To EditBox urtfeditbox (RichEditBox) Related Links $prompt Return or set the position for the cursor in the Form when the current ProcScript module ends. Auto Select (autoselect) Determines whether the text in the widget is selected when the field gets focus. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}